description:
Instrumental Truth is proud to present this beautiful and peaceful hymn. This "Karaoke/Instrumental" (Key : G) is sure to bring peace and serenity to your heart and soul. Listen and enjoy!

First Line : Master, the tempest is raging!
Title  : Peace! Be Still!
Author  : Mary Ann Baker
Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters' youtube channel.
